cs.SY, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.RO, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely category as the paper deals with controlling dynamical systems to satisfy temporal logic properties. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper uses linear temporal logic formulas to specify the desired behavior of the system. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper proposes an algorithm for solving the control problem. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper's approach could be applied to control robots. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper's approach involves solving a reachability problem using an automaton, which is a common technique in AI planning.
